  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will provide an educational intervention through means of a video to educate
      subjects on the risk of cardiovascular health on Rheumatoid arthritis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Subjects will be randomized into an interventional group and non-interventional group. Both
      groups will perform several surveys before an educational intervention may be given. Both
      Groups will come back 3 months post visit to complete additional surveys.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
